        <div class="mission-story">
            <h2>Acts 29 Mission Stories: Church Planting in Los Chilitos</h2>
            <p>As part of our outreach efforts, our church has partnered with organizations like <strong>Acts 29</strong> to support missions in remote regions such as <strong>Los Chilitos, Guatemala</strong>. In this small village, the gospel has been spread through hands-on evangelism, and we’ve had the privilege of helping baptize new believers and witness families and communities being transformed.</p>
            <p><a href="https://www.acts29.com/rural-guatemala-los-chilitos" target="_blank">Read more about the Acts 29 initiative in Los Chilitos</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="mission-story">
            <h2>The Gospel Coalition: A Story of Restoration</h2>
            <p>We’re also proud to highlight the efforts of Mitch & Amanda Muñoz, whose missionary journey in Los Chilitos is featured by The Gospel Coalition. Their work has resulted in significant spiritual and social growth in this area.</p>
            <p><a href="https://www.thegospelcoalition.org" target="_blank">Find the full story on The Gospel Coalition</a></p>
